description:
&lt;p&gt;We have six busy charity shops across Barking, Dagenham, Hornchurch and Upminster. Each shop relies onteams of volunteers to keep us trading. Our Retail Assistants work with the shop manager to prepare goods for sale, create window dressings and displays, assist customers, operate the cash register and process Gift Aid donations, as well as carrying out general housekeeping and cleaning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;What skills do we need?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for people who are friendly, polite and respectful and enjoy engaging with our customers. You will need to be punctual and reliable andwilling tolearn new skills and get involved. You also need to be able to work individually as well as part of a team. Experience of shop work is beneficial, but not essential, as training is provided.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;How much time will it take?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We operate on a flexible shift basis, with a shift usually lasting about 4 hours, or as agreed with the Shop Manager. At least one shift per week is ideal to keep your skills up to date and to assist with the running of the shop.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;What are the benefits?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will gain first-hand experience of working in a retail environment and understanding sales processes. You will also learn more about the charity sector. In addition, you will have an opportunity to build customer service and communication skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Location&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our shops are located at:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;29 Faircross Parade, Longbridge Road, Barking, IG11 8UW&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;37 The Broadway, Elm Park, Hornchurch, RM12 4RN&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;794 Green Lane, Dagenham, RM8 1YT&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5 Station Parade, Heathway, Dagenham, RM9 5AW&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4 Station Lane, Hornchurch, RM12 6NJ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;55 Corbets Tey Road, Upminster, RM14 2AJ&lt;/p&gt;
